A '''mood disorder''' or '''affective disorder''' is a type of [[mental illness]] where the main problem is the person's [[mood]].<ref>{{Harvnb | Sadock | 2002| p = 534}}</ref> The two main kinds of mood disorder are [[depressive disorder]]s (like [[major depressive disorder]]) and [[bipolar disorder]]. Some other mood disorders can be caused by using [[drug]]s.

